<!--
HTML page displaying a header, footer, and a filters box with dropdown.

Requirements:
- Use: header, footer, section, button, h3, h4, ul, li tags
- No inline style
- Do not use the img tag
- Do not use the style tag in the head tag
- All images must be stored in the images folder
- Must have 4 CSS files:
  - styles/4-common.css: for global style (body and .container styles)
  - styles/3-header.css: for header style
  - styles/3-footer.css: for footer style
  - styles/6-filters.css: for filters style
-->

index.html
styles/
  4-common.css
  3-header.css
  3-footer.css
  6-filters.css
images/
  logo.png
favicon.ico


